    "In addition, the platform is capable of performing under inert and lowpressure atmospheres, handling separation steps, and pressure sensing for reaction monitoring.",
    "Its efficacy and robustness were confirmed through the successful synthesis of five small organic molecules, four oligopeptides, and four oligonucleotides in high purity and impressive yield.",
