    "Figure 2d and has a lower throughput in comparison to other automated platforms, it does offer a low-cost alternative that can be adapted to perform chemical reaction optimization.In addition to academia, industry is increasingly recognizing the value of investing in custom-built HTE setups to automate their synthesis workflows for enhanced productivity."
